snippet.title: C.A.T.S. Gameplay Trailer
snippet.description:
C.A.T.S.: Crash Arena Turbo Stars, a new multiplayer title from the creators of Cut the Rope and King of Thieves, is coming to iOS & Android on April 20, 2017.

Pre-register on Google Play to be notified when the game is out: zep.tl/catspr

Visit our website: https://www.catsthegame.com

Want to learn more about C.A.T.S.?
Like us on Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/catsthegame
Follow us on Twitter: https://twitter.com/catsthegame
Check out our Instagram: @cats_the_game
Visit our VK page: https://vk.com/catsthegame
